"Led by Sara Silva from ECOLISE, this training guide was co-developed by the Global
Ecovillage Network Oceania and Asia and the Living Story Landscapes through Sarah
Queblatin, in close collaboration with Resilience.Earth through Erika Zárate and Oscar
